# =========================
# SnowyDeFAI public repo
# Day-1: README + LICENSE + /public only
# =========================

# Allowlist approach: ignore everything by default
*

# Then allow only what we want public
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE
!public/
!public/**

# (Optional) allow a docs folder later
#!docs/
#!docs/**

# Safety: never commit env/secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets.json
**/*.key
**/private/
**/wallet_data.txt
**/cookies.json
**/*.sqlite
**/*.db
**/logs/
